title: NPEB00342-[Resident Evil 4 HD Remaster][PS3][3K3y][Re-Upload]
description:
Game Title:  Resident Evil 4 [HD Remaster]
Platform:    PS3 [but originally for PS2]
Genre:       Survival Horror
Region:      USA [NTSC] & Region Free
Language:    English

	This game is a decrypted ISO built with ISO Tools made to be played on an OFW [No Keys] PS3 with 3K3y. It also works with CFW and 3K3y with encrypted ISOs. It even works on CFW without 3K3y. For CFW 3.55 or 4.21, just extract files, get fix if needed and load with BD mirror enabled. You should be able to get it working with Cobra and E3 as well with some tweaking.

Enjoy =D
